X-Lkml-Link: https://lkml.org/lkml/2007/9/10/318

This adds support for the Maple Bus - Sega's proprietary serial if
with peripherals - for the Dreamcast.
Signed-off by: Adrian McMenamin <adrian@mcmen.demon.co.uk>
